程序包 com.htsmart.wristband2.exceptions

  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    AckException
    The command was successfully sent to the wristband, but the wristband did not respond properly.
    AuthenticatedException
    Connect wristband and login mode, but some error occur.
    EcgStartFailedException
    Ecg testing start failed.
    GSensorStartFailedException
    Ecg testing start failed.
    OperationBusyException
    The operation queue is full, and can't add this new operation.
    PacketDataFormatException
    The PacketData format error.
    SyncBusyException
    Sync data in progress, so this operation can't be started.
    SyncStartFailedException
    Sync start failed.
    SyncTerminateException
    Error while synchronizing certain data.
    TemperatureRealTimeException
    This exception is thrown when an abnormal temperature measurement is interrupted。
    WristbandException
    Base class for wristband sdk exception
